msgid "Invite people to join this project"
msgstr "Gonbidatu jendea proiektuan parte hartzera"

msgid "Share an invitation link"
msgstr "Partekatu gonbidapen esteka"

msgid ""
"The easiest way to invite people is to give them the following invitation"
" link.<br />They will be able to access the project, manage participants,"
" add/edit/delete bills. However, they will not have access to important "
"settings such as changing the private code or deleting the whole project."
msgstr ""
"Jendea gonbidatzeko modurik errazena gonbidapen esteka hau ematea da. <br"
" />Proiektura sartu ahal izango dira, parte hartzaileak kudeatu, eta "
"fakturak gehitu/editatu/ezabatu. Hala ere, ez dute ezarpen "
"garrantzitsuetarako sarbiderik izango, hala nola kode pribatua aldatzea "
"edo proiektu osoa ezabatzea."

msgid "Scan QR code"
msgstr "QR kodea eskaneatu"

msgid "Use a mobile device with a compatible app."
msgstr "Erabili mugikor bat bateragarria den aplikazio batekin."

msgid "Send via Emails"
msgstr "Emailez bidali"

msgid ""
"Specify a list of email adresses (separated by comma) of people you want "
"to notify about the creation of this project. We will send them an email "
"with the invitation link."
msgstr ""
"Zehaztu posta elektronikoko helbideen zerrenda bat (koma bidez bereizita)"
" proiektu honen sorrerari buruz jakinarazteko. Mezu elektroniko bat "
"bidaliko zaie gonbidapenaren estekarekin."

msgid "Share Identifier & code"
msgstr "Partekatu identifikagailua eta kodea"

msgid ""
"You can share the project identifier and the private code by any "
"communication means.<br />Anyone with the private code will have access "
"to the full project, including changing settings such as the private code"
" or project email address, or even deleting the whole project."
msgstr ""
"Proiektuaren identifikatzailea eta kode pribatua partekatu ditzakezu "
"edozein komunikabideren bidez.<br />Kode pribatua duen edonork proiektu "
"osorako sarbidea izango du, ezarpenak aldatzeko aukera barne (hala nola "
"kode pribatua edo proiektuaren helbide elektronikoa, edo proiektu osoa "
"ezabatu)."

